*portage-prefpane-0.3.1 (01 Feb 2005)

  01 Feb 2005; Michael Hanselmann <hansmi@gentoo.org>
  +portage-prefpane-0.3.1.ebuild:
  New version, fixes a problem with use.default.

  18 Jan 2005; Michael Hanselmann <hansmi@gentoo.org>
  portage-prefpane-0.3-r1.ebuild:
  Stable on ppc-macos.

*portage-prefpane-0.3-r1 (11 Jan 2005)

  11 Jan 2005; Michael Hanselmann <hansmi@gentoo.org>
  +portage-prefpane-0.3-r1.ebuild:
  Added a small patch from MacShabba to make portage-prefpane understand
  FEATURES="autoconfig".

*portage-prefpane-0.3 (08 Dec 2004)

  08 Dec 2004; Michael Hanselmann <hansmi@gentoo.org>
  +portage-prefpane-0.3.ebuild:
  New version 0.3 with support for cascading profiles. Included now: editing
  FEATURES and GENTOO_MIRRORS. Fixed many bugs.

*portage-prefpane-0.2 (21 Sep 2004)

  21 Sep 2004; Michael Hanselmann <hansmi@gentoo.org>
  +portage-prefpane-0.2.ebuild:
  New version 0.2.

*portage-prefpane-0.1-r1 (21 Aug 2004)

  21 Aug 2004; Michael Hanselmann <hansmi@gentoo.org>
  +portage-prefpane-0.1-r1.ebuild:
  Fixed a link-error during removing '-lObjC' with sed.

*portage-prefpane-0.1 (21 Aug 2004)

  21 Aug 2004; Michael Hanselmann <hansmi@gentoo.org> : portage-prefpane-0.1.ebuild
  Added version 0.1 to portage. It is only experimental by now.

